                        <note rend="inline" type="source">721.23/2158: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Ambassador in Peru</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Dearing</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-03-30T11:00:00-05:00">March 30, 1934—11
                                a.m.</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>27. Your 37, March 27, 10 a.m., paragraph 11. Please send brief cable
                            reports on developments of interest in the Leticia situation.</p>
